981
00:58:28,920 --> 00:58:30,990
Tell Big Daddy what happened.

982
00:58:31,200 --> 00:58:32,633
Go on, tell him.

983
00:58:32,840 --> 00:58:34,671
You're a sports announcer.

984
00:58:34,880 --> 00:58:39,032
