1019
01:00:10,240 --> 01:00:12,117
I'd get rid of Skipper.

1020
01:00:12,320 --> 01:00:15,915
I'd show Brick that their deep,
true friendship was a big lie.

1021
01:00:16,600 --> 01:00:17,953
