1033
01:00:45,200 --> 01:00:47,714
Supposing I lost you instead?

1034
01:00:48,520 --> 01:00:51,432
Supposing you'd hate me
instead of Skipper?

1035
01:00:52,360 --> 01:00:54,112
So I ran.

1036
01:00:54,880 --> 01:00:56,154
Nothing happened!

1037
01:00:56,360 --> 01:00:59,158
