but he won't let me.

1038
01:00:59,760 --> 01:01:00,988
Nothing happened!

1039
01:01:01,200 --> 01:01:03,316
Hallelujah, St. Maggie.

1040
01:01:05,040 --> 01:01:07,395
I wanted to get rid of Skipper.

1041
01:01:08,240 --> 01:01:09,912
