"Why did Brick hang up on me?"

1055
01:01:58,920 --> 01:02:00,672
Why, Brick?

1056
01:02:15,440 --> 01:02:17,670
BlG DADDY: Where are you going?
BRlCK: Home.

1057
01:02:20,520 --> 01:02:23,159
-You can't drive. You're drunk.
-Not yet, Big Daddy.

1058
01:02:23,240 --> 01:02:25,470
BRlCK: Not yet. Now, give me that bottle.

1059
01:02:26,160 --> 01:02:27,752
[Sound of breaking glass]

1060
01:02:29,000 --> 01:02:30,718
What are you running away from?

1061
01:02:35,040 --> 01:02:38,112
